### Enclosure Design Specifications

```
ENCLOSURE SPECIFICATIONS
=======================

MATERIALS:
- Main body: PETG or PLA (3D printed)
- Optional: Aluminum (CNC machined)
- Color: Black (recommended)

DIMENSIONS:
- Width: 120mm
- Depth: 90mm  
- Height: 35mm
- Wall thickness: 2.5mm

CUTOUTS:
- Front: 
  - Power button (12mm)
  - LED indicators (3x 3mm)
  - UART port (10mm x 8mm)
- Side:
  - USB ports (4x 15mm x 8mm)
  - HDMI port (15mm x 5mm)
  - Ethernet port (15mm x 10mm)
  - Power input (10mm x 5mm)
- Top:
  - Cooling vents (80mm x 40mm)
  - Fan mounting (40mm x 40mm)
- Bottom:
  - GPIO access (60mm x 30mm)
  - Mounting holes (4x M2.5)
  - Rubber feet (4x 10mm)

MOUNTING:
- 4x M2.5 mounting holes
- 4x rubber feet (10mm diameter)
- Wall mount option: 2x keyhole slots

COOLING:
- Passive: Top vents (80mm x 40mm)
- Active: Optional 40mm fan
- Airflow: Bottom to top

ACCESS:
- Removable top panel
- Tool-less GPIO access
- Front panel with indicator cutouts

WEIGHT:
- Approx 200g (with Pi installed)
- Approx 350g (with full system)
```

